data.description: LOCATION!  LOCATION!  This 3 bedroom 2 bath CBS home is located stones throw to Lee Blvd and not far from SR 82.  Home features 1,955 +/- sq ft of living area, with garage and screened porch, has total area of 2,452 +/-. Master bedroom is oversized, with a bathroom that has dual sinks and shower only.  The other 2 bedrooms are just a roomy and guest bath with tub/shower combo.   Kitchen has plenty of cabinets and space for all those family dinners and get togethers.  If that's not enough space, you will love the large family room and living room.   Rear of property is fenced.   Don't miss out, make your appointment today!!!
